data.name: textName.ToolTip
data.value: The name Skyline will use to refer to this library

data.name: textPath.ToolTip
data.value: Location on disk at which the final non-redundant library will be created.

data.name: comboAction.ToolTip
data.value: Choose to create a new library or append to an existing library, if you have previously saved a copy of the redundant library data.

data.name: cbIncludeAmbiguousMatches.ToolTip
data.value: Check to keep spectra that match multiple peptides.

data.name: cbKeepRedundant.ToolTip
data.value: Check to keep a copy of the redundant library to which you can append more spectra in the future.

data.name: cbFilter.ToolTip
data.value: Check to filter matches for only the peptides in the document.

data.name: btnAddDirectory.ToolTip
data.value: Add all acceptable spectrum files found below a root directory. You can uncheck ones you do not want added to the library.

data.name: btnAddFile.ToolTip
data.value: Add a file or multiple files from a single directory.
